OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,FTottenham's Kevin Danso tells ITV News
OL,7,FSports Editor Steve Scott how he'd
OL,8,Fkept quiet about racism he'd suffered
OL,9,Fin the past` but felt compelled to
OL,10,Fspeak out over a wave of abuse he
OL,11,Freceived last month if anything is to
OL,12,Fchange in the football world
OL,14,FTottenham Hotspur's international
OL,15,Fdefender Kevin Danso admits the racial
OL,16,Fabuse he received recently hurt him.
OL,18,F"I'm only human. People make mistakes,
OL,19,Fand I feel like people shouldn't be
OL,20,Fjudged or discriminated against
OL,21,Fbecause they've made a mistake.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"I'm proud of who I am. It's not nice,
OL,7,Fbut it's not something that I want to
OL,8,Fgo through again. But I think the main
OL,9,Fthing is it just doesn't define me,
OL,10,Fand it doesn't belong in the world of
OL,11,Ffootball."
OL,13,FThe mistake he's talking about is a
OL,14,Fmoment every footballer experiences `
OL,15,Falmost in every game.
OL,17,FBut this particular one, right at the
OL,18,Fend of a match against Brighton, led
OL,19,Fto a goal that harmed Spurs' Premier
OL,20,FLeague survival hopes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,FSoon afterwards, his social media
OL,7,Finbox lit up with racist messages and
OL,8,Femojis. So, after a few weeks of
OL,9,Freflection, what would he say to those
OL,10,Fwho reached for their phones to attack
OL,11,Fhim?
OL,13,F"It doesn't make me feel good. I don't
OL,14,Fknow if that makes you feel good, but
OL,15,Fit's not the solution, and there's
OL,16,Fjust no need for it, and I understand
OL,17,Fyou're upset for whatever reason, but
OL,18,Fan eye for an eye is never the
OL,19,Fsolution.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"It doesn't make the situation better;
OL,7,Fit's quite the opposite. It makes it
OL,8,Fworse, and it says more about that
OL,9,Fperson than what it says about me."
OL,11,FIntellectually and emotionally, Danso
OL,12,Fis certainly more than a match for the
OL,13,Fracists who targeted him.
OL,15,FHe is fluent in several languages and
OL,16,Fhas lived and worked in many European
OL,17,Fcountries, which in part is why his
OL,18,Fresponse to the abuse he suffered is
OL,19,Fnot angry, but measured.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"I grew up in Austria, facing racism
OL,7,Fquite a fair bit, being in a
OL,8,Fpredominantly white country, but again
OL,9,FI think I've learnt how to deal with
OL,10,Fit in a way.
OL,12,F"It doesn't define me. It's their
OL,13,Fproblem, and I just try to ignore it
OL,14,Fas much as I can or try to not ignore
OL,15,Fit but not let it have as much of an
OL,16,Feffect on me and what I feel about
OL,17,Fmyself and how I feel about myself and
OL,18,Fmy performance in order to continue to
OL,19,Fplay at a very high level."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,FBut he admits he knows players whose
OL,7,Fperformances suffer because of racism,
OL,8,Fespecially younger professionals.
OL,10,F"I think when growing up, we played in
OL,11,FGermany in the youth system where
OL,12,Fplayers did suffer that racism from a
OL,13,Fyoung age and playing their first few
OL,14,Fgames as professionals.
OL,16,F"I think it kind of set them back and
OL,17,Fyou know I think it's hurtful like I
OL,18,Fsaid it definitely is hurtful and it
OL,19,Fhas a negative impact."
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
