PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,FDanso experienced the same as a
OL,7,Fyoungster and kept it to himself.
OL,9,F"It was in Germany, and that was tough
OL,10,Fas well, but I was very young and I
OL,11,Fdidn't tell anybody about it. I didn't
OL,12,Fspeak out because I didn't want to
OL,13,Fmake it a big thing.
OL,15,F"I remember it was a game against
OL,16,FBayern Munich (and I) had a clash with
OL,17,FKingsley Coman, and the Bayern fans
OL,18,Fwere just flooding my messages -
OL,19,Fsending like monkey emojis, stuff like
OL,20,Fthat. And I didn't tell anybody.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOUxD@OpmxD@Upn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"The next time you played Bayern,
OL,7,Fyou'd always go into the tackle, maybe
OL,8,Fnot as hard as you would normally."
OL,10,FAfter the Brighton game, his mindset
OL,11,Fwas very different. This time, he
OL,12,Fbelieved people needed to know about
OL,13,Fwhat came his way, if anything was
OL,14,Fgoing to change.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"I feel like this time it was
OL,7,Fimportant to say something, to just
OL,8,Faddress it and make sure that people
OL,9,Fare aware I've seen it and it doesn't
OL,10,Fdefine who I am, and it's not going to
OL,11,Fmake me play any different and
OL,12,Fdefinitely there's no need for it and
OL,13,Fbasically you're wasting your time."
OL,15,FRacists who targeted England's Lioness
OL,16,FJess Carter and Manchester City's
OL,17,FAntoine Semenyo have been charged with
OL,18,Fcriminal offences this season; Danso
OL,19,Fbelieves that level of punishment will
OL,20,Fhelp in the fight against this type of
OL,21,Fabuse.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"I think they should definitely suffer
OL,7,Fthe most severe consequence you can
OL,8,Ffor that situation because I think
OL,9,Fonly then people would realise what
OL,10,Fthey're doing is actually wrong, and
OL,11,Fthen hopefully it happens less and
OL,12,Fless."
OL,14,F"Sometimes it's just educating people
OL,15,Fon why you shouldn't and what effect
OL,16,Fit can have on people and (then it's)
OL,17,Fprison if they continue to do it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@FO]vD@AOUxD@[pmxD@epn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"I never wish anything negative or
OL,7,Fextreme bad things to happen to
OL,8,Fanybody but I think the bare minimum
OL,9,Fis definitely just to be educated on
OL,10,Fwhat racism is how it can affect
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,F"Even just to have a look and learn
OL,14,Fabout history not too long ago, what
OL,15,Fhappened and why it's such a big issue
OL,16,For why it's such a sensitive topic."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
