OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,FAfter the recent abuse aimed at Danso,
OL,7,FTottenham Hotspur described the
OL,8,Fmessages as "vile, dehumanising
OL,9,Fracism" and reported them to the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,F"I think with the support I got from
OL,13,Fthe club, from my family, from even
OL,14,Fjust fans on the street just saying
OL,15,Fthat 100% behind me and I don't
OL,16,Fdeserve that. It was amazing, you know
OL,17,Fthat kind of helped me get through it."
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@GO]tD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,FDepressingly, the leading anti-
OL,7,Fdiscrimination group Kick it Out says
OL,8,Fincidents of racism within stadia and
OL,9,Fonline are not dropping; in fact,
OL,10,Facross the entire sport, from
OL,11,Fgrassroots up to the professional
OL,12,Fgame, they are heading for a record
OL,13,Fnumber of reports by the end of the
OL,14,Fseason.
OL,16,FThe abuse Danso suffered also came
OL,17,Fduring the Premier League's 'No Room
OL,18,Ffor Racism' weekend; so, does he
OL,19,Fbelieve campaigns and slogans are
OL,20,Fineffective, or are they worthwhile?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"I think the Premier League does raise
OL,7,F(a) tremendous amount of awareness,
OL,8,Fand I feel like all of football, and
OL,9,Fplayers can do is continue to raise
OL,10,Fawareness, to continue to take a stand
OL,11,Fagainst it, and you know just teach
OL,12,Fthese people that it shouldn't happen.
OL,14,F"I think people who do racially abuse
OL,15,Fyou, I don't believe that most of them
OL,16,Fare racist, but they're hurt and they
OL,17,Fwant to do something that kind of gets
OL,18,Fto you as a person."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@ApmoD@CpnvD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
