PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBy nature, it seems that Danso is not
OL,12,Fonly thoughtful, but incredibly
OL,13,Fforgiving.
OL,15,F"I always try to put myself in
OL,16,Fsomebody else's shoes and be like
OL,17,F'Okay, what's the reason why they're
OL,18,Freacting in the way they're reacting?'.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1778551406
OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,F"But honestly, it doesn't make the
OL,7,Fsituation better, it's quite the
OL,8,Fopposite, it makes it worse and they
OL,9,Flook quite silly for doing it because
OL,10,Fit says more about that person than it
OL,11,Fsays about me."
OL,13,FDanso has been and will continue to be
OL,14,Fa key part of a Tottenham team that is
OL,15,Ffighting for its Premier League
OL,16,Fsurvival. He is also hoping to play in
OL,17,Fthis summer's World Cup for Austria.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
