OL,3,C'It's their problem': Tottenham's
OL,4,CKevin Danso opens up on racist abuse
OL,6,FBy then, if there's any justice, those
OL,7,Fwho targeted Danso might well be
OL,8,Fwatching him at the tournament with a
OL,9,Fcriminal conviction to their name.
